728
00:32:06,684 --> 00:32:08,018
(SIGHS)

729
00:32:09,687 --> 00:32:11,814
Oh, I wanna get back on TV.

730
00:32:14,149 --> 00:32:16,527
I'm going back to work for you.

731
00:32:18,696 --> 00:32:20,698
